Split {TOP,BOTTOM}_LAYER into {TOP,BOTTOM}_{SILK_LAYER,SIDE} depending on usage

We used the previous constants to identify board sides, as well as an offset
after all copper layers to find the silk-screen layers. Split the usage to
keep useage as a board SIDE integer and LAYER offset separate.


